The room was large, the bed was oh so comfortable, the shower was really nice and we liked having a fridge in the room.	The hotel was very clean, room was quite large and shower had good water pressure.	The rooms are modern, very clean and have many more amenities than one expects, including fridge, microwave, large HDTV, adjustable bed, spacious bathroom and, if upgrading, a wonderful Jacuzzi.	The whirpool was great - it is located in the bedroom rather than the bathroom and was big enough for two!